data.description: Discover this impressive 1.5-story home nestled on a spacious 1-acre lot without the confines of a subdivision. With its elevated 9-foot ceilings and a wealth of upgrades, this residence is a true gem. Designed to be an entertainer's delight, you can seamlessly enjoy the dining area, kitchen, breakfast nook, and living room all in one expansive space. Step inside to be greeted by stunning laminate floors that grace the main living areas, while the bedrooms offer cozy carpets and the bathrooms feature elegant tiled flooring. The kitchen and dining area shine with upgraded lighting fixtures, and the aesthetic appeal continues with granite countertops adorning both the kitchen and bathrooms. The main level boasts a generous master suite complete with a roomy walk-in closet. The master bathroom offers a touch of luxury with his and her sinks, a separate garden tub, and an upgraded shower door enclosing the tiled shower.
